"settings_smart_notifications_sheet_body" = "Intelligent notifications adjust reminders based on how much you have already drunk throughout the day.\n\nInstead of notifying only by time, the app considers your daily goal, the active reminder window, and your current progress.\n\nIf you have already reached the expected amount by that moment, the reminder is automatically silenced.\n\nAlso, if you log water a few minutes before a reminder, we avoid sending a redundant notification right after.\n\nThe goal is to remind you when you really need it, reducing interruptions and making reminders more useful.";
